# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# CONFIGURAÇÕES OBRIGATÓRIAS
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# Token do bot (Discord Developer Portal)
DISCORD_TOKEN=seu_token_aqui

# URI do MongoDB (MongoDB Atlas ou local)
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://usuario:senha@cluster.mongodb.net/nomedb?retryWrites=true&w=majority

# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# CONFIGURAÇÕES DO BOT
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# Prefixo dos comandos
PREFIX=!

# ID do dono do bot (seu Discord ID)
OWNER_ID=seu_discord_id_aqui

# ID do servidor principal
GUILD_ID=id_do_servidor_aqui

# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# CARGOS (IDs separados por vírgula)
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# IDs dos cargos de staff (podem usar comandos moderação)
STAFF_ROLES=id_cargo_mod,id_cargo_suporte

# IDs dos cargos de admin
ADMIN_ROLES=id_cargo_admin,id_cargo_ceo

# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# CANAIS ESPECIAIS (IDs)
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

LOG_CHANNEL=id_canal_logs
MOD_LOG_CHANNEL=id_canal_logs_mod
WELCOME_CHANNEL=id_canal_boas_vindas
DATING_CHANNEL=id_canal_namoro
DUO_CHANNEL=id_canal_duo
DARK_LOVE_CHANNEL=id_canal_dark_love
CONFESSIONS_CHANNEL=id_canal_confissoes
RANKINGS_CHANNEL=id_canal_rankings

# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# CATEGORIAS (IDs)
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

TICKET_CATEGORY=id_categoria_tickets
PRIVATE_CALL_CATEGORY=id_categoria_calls
